	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hi, can you switch Nestopia for MacOS to PAL? (using MacOS Version 1.4.1 here...)<br />I cannot find any option for PAL/NTSC in the settings.  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_eek.gif" alt=":shock:" title="Shocked" />  Or is there any trick to force PAL?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


