		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Oh, you're right, there's a PAL bit in the NES header!  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_redface.gif" alt=":oops:" title="Embarassed" /><br />Setting that bit works perfectly, thanks!

		

		</td>
	</tr>
